<body>
<div>
<p xml:id="subtitle1" begin="2331910000t" end="2371530000t" region="region0" style="style6">（隼人）なるほどな<br/>"<span style="style7"><span style="style8">炎刃旋風</span><span style="style9">えんじんせんぷう</span></span>"か</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle2" begin="2372360000t" end="2398220000t" region="region0" style="style6">その<span style="style7"><span style="style8">能力</span><span style="style9">ちから</span></span>を<br/>両腕に集中させて</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle3" begin="2399060000t" end="2421160000t" region="region0" style="style6">攻撃速度を上げとるんか</p>
<p xml:id="subtitle4" begin="2432010000t" end="2473300000t" region="region0" style="style0"><span style="style1">残念　こっちは</span><br/><span style="style1">防御前提で構えとんねん</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle5" begin="2486230000t" end="2523350000t" region="region0" style="style0"><span style="style1">君 しつこいから</span><br/><span style="style1">最終手段を使わせてもらうで</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle6" begin="2524180000t" end="2560050000t" region="region0" style="style0"><span style="style3"><span style="style4">氷結障壁</span><span style="style5">ひょうけつしょうへき</span></span><span style="style1">やし</span><br/><span style="style1">回復は お手のもんやろ</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle7" begin="2560890000t" end="2592170000t" region="region0" style="style0"><span style="style1">回復に気ぃ回しながら</span><br/><span style="style1">どこまで 俺とやれるか</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle8" begin="2593000000t" end="2610100000t" region="region0" style="style0"><span style="style1">試してみよか</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle9" begin="2610940000t" end="2641800000t" region="region0" style="style0"><span style="style1">-（涼太）用意がいいな</span><br/><span style="style1">-（隼人）内緒やで</span></p>
<p xml:id="subtitle10" begin="2642640000t" end="2663070000t" region="region0" style="style0"><span style="style1">ぶっちゃけ</span><br/><span style="style1">まだ本気出してへんねん</span></p>
</div>
</body>
</tt>
